{"tid":585620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵期望6月再加價   加幅達3%","createTime":"2018-03-08T23:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T02:26:00.000Z","uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"282e71b0304d02a5ee95c5f128bb07a79cf7f33a","tid":585620,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T23:58:42.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日公布業績，去年盈利按年上升64%至168.3億元，為近10年以來新高，反映港鐵公司財務穩健和發展理想。根據現行可加可減機制、統計處去年公布的通脹率1.7%加幅，以及將於今個月底公布的運輸業工資指數，連同去年度未啟動的1.49%加幅，港鐵公司有機會於今年6月再次加價，而幅度更可能高達3%水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民建聯期望港鐵在盈利豐厚的情況下，仿效特區政府回饋市民的做法，並建議豁免未啟動的1.49%票價加幅，並將今年度分享利潤機制下必須回贈乘客的2億2千250萬元，以及推出補貼優惠，如「九七折車費扣減」優惠至整個財政年度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1158769/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1158769%2F&d=%2BifJll7jf7hpqqx4FsLUgG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8d90ada6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1158769%2F&h=5c992dcc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1158769/</a>"},{"pid":"58d09361e7f40f8fba4cd5e472cb2126926ddb43","tid":585620,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"又話比幾億優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57fb161b13c2b4ac4e1e8716e9186a5bbbc3500","tid":585620,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T23:59:39.000Z","msg":"幾時先升呀 屌"},{"pid":"266329be0c0b6aa1695acc8fc129a045daee1857","tid":585620,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58d09361e7f40f8fba4cd5e472cb2126926ddb43","tid":585620,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"又話比幾億優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"